description: My place is close to Bloomingdales. You’ll love my place because of The Upper East Side location, the people and easy access to several subways such as: 4, 5, 6, N, Q, R, and the F train.  Close to the local grocery store, Whole Foods is only a few blocks away and a Duane Reade is on the corner.  You are 4 blocks to Central Park.
name: Sun drenched lg. studio alcove renovated UES
